{"id":310,"date":"2013-05-28T19:38:26","date_gmt":"2013-05-28T19:38:26","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/sweetmediasolutions.com\/sfi\/?page_id=310"},"modified":"2025-10-16T12:47:10","modified_gmt":"2025-10-16T19:47:10","slug":"meeting-schedule","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/meeting-schedule\/","title":{"rendered":"Meeting Schedule"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>This page is where you can find our meeting schedule for SFI Spec Review Committees.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/section_divider_up.png\" alt=\"\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #269cd8;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">2025 SFI Committee Spec Review Meetings<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p>SFI Foundation, Inc (SFI) requires that existing specifications be reviewed on a periodic basis to ensure that the specs remain current to changing field conditions. We are holding SFI spec review meetings at the PRI Show in December 2025 in Indianapolis, Indiana, USA. All times listed are local, eastern time zone.<\/p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 18.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; color: #333333;\">All meetings listed below will be held at the following location:<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 18.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; color: #333333;\">Performance Racing Industry Trade Show<br \/>\nIndiana Convention Center<br \/>\n100 South Capitol, Indianapolis, IN 46225<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 18.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; color: #333333;\"><strong>Meeting Room: 204 (note new room location this year)<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/pdfs\/SFI-PRIMeetings2025.pdf\">Click here<\/a> to download a PDF of the <a href=\"http:\/\/sfifoundation.com\/wp-content\/pdfs\/SFI-PRIMeetings2025.pdf\">SFI Meeting Schedule 2025<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 18.0pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; color: #269cd